Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,情况就是\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The fact is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这些房贷证券…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That these mortgage backed securities
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有相当高风险的可调利率房贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Are filled with extremely risky sub-prime adjustable rates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等这部分到07年左右开始发作\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and when the majority of these adjustable rates kick in.... in '07
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,市场就会衰退\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They will begin to fail
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果最终能占到15%以上 整个房贷证券市场就毫无价值\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and if they fail above 15 percent the whole bond is worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克，停下来再想想，回头我再找你聊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-Michael, just take a beat, we'll talk about this later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,劳伦斯，别给我来这套…如果…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Lawrence please, don't patronize me, if ... it .. is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷证券，次级贷，份额…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-Mortgage backed securities, sub-prime loans, tranches....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,名词让人头疼是吧？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Is pretty confusing right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是让你觉得智商特别低\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Doesn't it make you feel bored.... or stupid....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是它的本意\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well... it's  supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,华尔街特别爱用玄乎的词儿，让你觉得只有他们才能做的来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Wall-street loves to use confusing terms, to make you think only they can do what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你撒手不管\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Or even better.....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就更高兴了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}for you just to leave them the fuck alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们让演员玛格在泡泡浴里解释给你听\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So... here's Margot Robbie in a bubble-bath to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大概意思就是，刘易斯的房贷证券 让大银行疯狂赚钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Basically, Lewis Rainieri's mortgage bonds were amazingly profitable for the big banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:14:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从2%的买卖提成中赚了几十亿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They made billions and billions off of their 2% fee they got for selling each of these bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但慢慢房贷不够用来组成证券了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But then they start ranning out of mortgages to put in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟房子和能买房的人都是有数儿的，对吧？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}After all, there are only so many homes and so many people with good enough jobs to buy them... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,银行就开始把风险越来越高的房贷做成证券\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So the banks started filling these bonds with riskier and riskier mortgages
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了，亨利\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Thank you Hendry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话，机器就能一直转着了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That way, they can keep that profit machine churning right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，这些高风险的房贷，就叫：次级贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}By the way, these risky mortgages are called: Sub-Prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下回，听到次级贷这个词，你就想：狗屎贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So... whenever you hear sub-prime... think: Shit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克老兄发现…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Our friend Michael Burry found out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这些房贷证券\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}that these mortgages bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,本来应该至少有65%的3A评级 但其实里面就是一坨屎\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}that were supposedly 65 percent AAA, were actually just, basically full of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他要做空房贷证券\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So now he's going to short the bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是…赌房产市场跌\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}which means.... Bet against.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吧？太好了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Got it?.... Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别看姐洗澡了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Now fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很快人们就会发现这个机会的，咱们得快点干\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's only a matter of time before someone else sees this investment, we have to act now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么就知道这些证券不值钱？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How do you know the bonds are worthless?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面不是有上千页房贷吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Aren't they filled with fucking thousands of pages of mortgages?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我都看了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I read them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你都看了？ - 我都看了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-You read them? I read.... Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没人这么脑子进水，打包房贷的证券律师才不得不看\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No-one reads them, only the lawyers who put them together read them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们也不懂纸里包的是什么\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't think they even know what they've made
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有这些垃圾贷款，房地产注定火不起来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The housing market is propped up on these bad loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,定时炸弹在，我要做空房产市场\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's a time-bomb and i want to short it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,凭借什么做空？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Through what instrument Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还没有做房贷证券的保险或期权\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}There are no insurance-contracts or options for mortgage bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这证券太稳定没人做！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The bonds are too stable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,劳伦斯…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Lawrence....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算这么干…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This is what I'm gonna do....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让银行，专门为我做一个金融工具\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I am gonna get a bank to make me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Then.....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我再买下来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm gonna buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不做这种买卖\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't want that kind of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这钱不干净，是黑心钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Money is not money! That's bad money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！看着点！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hey... Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:16:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你，什么公司这么玩弄客户 还能做大？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Let me ask you this: What company treats its customers that shittily and succeeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…高盛银行…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fine... OK... Goldman....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,马克不信任何人\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Without proving it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他小的时候在犹太学院学法典时\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}When he was a kid he excelled at studying the Talmud and Yeshiva.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,废话少说，有天他老师对说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Whatever! But, one day his Rabbi told his mom why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗不错，马克学习法典也成绩优异\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Paul is a fine boy and Mark is an excellent student of the Torah and Talmud
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那还有什么问题，老师？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Then what's the problem Rabbi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为马克努力学习的理由\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's the reason Mark is studying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他是想要找到上帝福音中的矛盾之处！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He's looking for inconsistencies in the word of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那他找到了吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So has he found any?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,以后，马克就在华尔街成立了自己的基金\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Later Baum started his own fund on Wall-street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他对屁话可是有狗一样嗅觉\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He had an amazing nose for bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里有蠢蛋在胡说，他都会给大伙指出来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He wasn't afraid to let anyone know, when and where the bull had gone number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,后来马克经历了不幸，整个世界观都阴暗了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Then a tragedy happened to Mark and it turned his whole world really dark
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,开始觉得整个金融系统都是骗局\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and ready to believe the whole system was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,辛西娅找我，我20分钟到办公室\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's Cynthia, I'll be in the office in twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hi Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咨询师打电话给我，你怎么又这样了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The therapist called.... You did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没出租车有什么办法\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}There were no cabs... What was i supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我很担心你的状态\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I worry about you Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我至少去报到了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}At least i went
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样，像是想把全世界都理顺了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're running around like you have to right every wrong in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧… - 一直气鼓鼓的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-Ok... -How angry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对！我就是心眼小，现在还生气了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fine! You know what... I'm a mean guy and I'm pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可我这个圈子，留下烂摊子 擦屁股走人的太多\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But... It is a shitstorm out here sweetie. You have no idea the kind of crap people are pulling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙还脸上自带拍恩雅MTV的表情\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and everybody is walking around like they're in a goddamn Enya-video.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,以后他们全被玩完\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They're all getting screwed you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们关心什么？关心球赛！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You know what they care about? They care about the ballgame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,关心哪个女演员去戒毒了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Or they care about what actresses went into rehab!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你得让医生给你开点药了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I, I think you should try medication!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，咱俩商量过，影响工作的药不能吃\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, no, we agreed, if it interfered with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么恨华尔街，消消气就别干了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}you hate Wall-street, but maybe it's time to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爱这一行！- 你恨这一行！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I love my job! -You hate your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爱这一行！- 你都这么郁闷了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I love my job! -You're miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱我的工作，真的！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I love my job, I love my job honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,马克！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,想起发生的事情，我每天也心里不舒服\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I am sad every day about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定也不好受，可你从来不表现出来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I know you must feel the same, but you never show it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们兄弟俩关系很好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I knew how close you were to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,卡布！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}CAB!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Where'd ya go pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,卡布！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}CAB!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,每天我都觉得你想开口聊聊，可你总是忍着\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Everyday i think you're gonna talk about it, and you never do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你能试着做一点改变吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Will you ever think about the idea of making a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，亲爱的，我会认真考虑的…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fine, fine, honey, you know what, i will consider it, but honestly....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我真的没事儿，放心\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Cynthia I'm OK, I really am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿！这是我抢来的出租\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hey, Hey! No, no, my cab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的出租！我的！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's my cab, that's my cab, That is my cab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蠢货！ - 滚蛋！ - 你滚蛋！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-Schmuck! -Fuck you! -Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我等会再打给你\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我要买…房贷证券的互换\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I wanna buy.... swaps on mortgage bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这种信用违约互换，来担保\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Credit default swap, that will pay off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷证券不能兑换的情况\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}If the underlying.... bond fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想要赌房价跌？ - 是的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-You want to bet against the housing market? Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  高盛公司\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} Goldman Sachs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,除非有上百万的美国人房贷断供才有可能\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Those bonds only fail if millions of Americans don't pay their mortgages.
