Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.02,0:26:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好像下面兜着个口袋一样\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And is like a sack underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.59,0:26:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我的附睾清晰可见 （附睾发炎）\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Inflamed epididymis I have an extremely pronounced epididymis
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.78,0:26:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,肿得和睾丸一样大\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Almost as large as another testicle on itself
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.45,0:26:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们听我说，辛西娅…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So get this.... Cynthia.. Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.14,0:26:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我辞职不干了！ 让我在佛蒙特州开个过夜旅馆\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Cynthia wants me to quit! And open a B&B in Vermont.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.16,0:26:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的主意！我挺想看你会怎么开旅馆\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's great! I'd love to see Mark Baum run a Bed and Breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.64,0:26:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,估计是这样：吃你的燕麦粥吧，傻逼！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Like: Here's your steel-cut oatmeal asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.65,0:26:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,马克不愿意讨好那些能开出支票的顾客\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mark refused to kiss the ring of the people with the checkbooks,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.51,0:27:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才委屈自己在摩根士丹利旗下开设基金\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}so he had to set up his fund under Morgan Stanley's umbrella.
