Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.09,0:27:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一群变态！变态！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You guys are sick.. You're sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.72,0:27:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她说，这工作让我不爽\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}She says, this job is making me unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.91,0:27:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可你不爽的时候反倒挺爽的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-But you're happy when you're unhappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.22,0:27:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在不爽的时候感觉挺爽的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I am happy when I'm unhappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.50,0:27:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,文尼·丹尼尔 - 你知道怎么做松饼吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Vinny Daniel -You know how to make a muffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.87,0:27:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,文尼是马克手下懂数字的人\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mark's numbers guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.41,0:27:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你连怎么洗衣服都不知道吧？铺床呢？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Do you even know how to do laundry? Make a bed? -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.22,0:27:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,文尼小的时候，爸爸就因为一场恶性犯罪去世了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Vinny lost his father to a violent crime when he was young
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.83,0:27:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,和马克一样，他也从来不说起这事\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Just like Mark, he didn't talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.71,0:27:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是不说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-I don't talk about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.33,0:27:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,辛西娅这么认真，还真有可能赶他到佛蒙特州去\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Cynthia's no joke, she could actually make him move to Vermont!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.48,0:27:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她都逼着我穿西服了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I mean, she made me start wearing a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.71,0:27:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,伯特·柯林斯，布朗大学的奥运会级别划船手\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Porter Collins, former Olympic rower, went to Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.42,0:27:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,从上一个公司和马克一起过来 搞不懂为什么没人听马克的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He worked with Baum at a previous firm, and couldn't figure out why no-one listened to Baum.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.08,0:27:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得马克提出的都是好点子\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The guy with all the good ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.16,0:27:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是打错电话了？ 这里还有个叫顶尖基金的公司？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Sir, yeah, i know, do you have the wrong FrontPoint? Cause there is another front-point in this same building that is Baum's
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.15,0:27:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼·摩西，是这群人里的乐天派\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And Danny Moses, the optimist of the bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.08,0:27:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他是交易鬼才 也这是大伙容忍他傻瓜式乐天派的唯一原因\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And a hell of a trader, which is the only reason they put up with his bullshit optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.38,0:27:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计，你对打错电话的也太客气了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're a weird caller, you take longer with a wrong number than anybody else
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.52,0:27:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙是德意志银行的，说什么做空房贷证券\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I mean... it's this guy... from... Deutsche, who was talking about shorting housing bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.60,0:28:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,说到中间，我才听出他找错人了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And then, in the middle of the call where I had realized he had the wrong front-point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.19,0:28:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他说想要找8层的那个公司\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and then... and then... cause he wanted the one on the eighth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.24,0:28:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他想要做空房贷证券？- 嗯\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He wanted to short housing bonds? - Hmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.28,0:28:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,每天至少5个拨错的电话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-It happens like five times a day, that somebody uses the wrong front-point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.79,0:28:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们得改个名了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We should change our name!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.42,0:28:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等，他想要做空房贷证券？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Wait, wait... He wanted to short housing bonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.07,0:28:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,赌房价跌吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Who bets against housing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.90,0:28:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 资产担保证券指数到几点了？- 这指数什么意思？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}- What's the ABX at? - What's ABX?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.51,0:28:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 用来跟踪次级房贷证券的价值 - 快睡你的觉！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-It tracks sub-prime mortgage bond value. -Go back to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.75,0:28:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,指数在…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The ABX is at ... eh....
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.52,0:28:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天！降下来了，去年到现在降了3点 这不对劲\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Wow! it's down, It's down 3 points since last year, that's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.23,0:28:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么一点动静都没听到过\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I haven't heard a peep about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.96,0:28:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这人叫啥？杰瑞德…威内特\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What was this guys name? Jared Vennett... Vennett
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.65,0:28:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的！这群中奖了的杂种因为我拨错的电话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's right! These lucky sons of bitches caught wind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住了华尔街历史上最好的一桩交易\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}of one of the best trades in Wall-street history from a wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.14,0:28:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们应该给我的错误电话线路抽成10%\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They should've paid 10 percent to my fuck up state system
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.91,0:28:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,叫杰瑞德·威内特\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He was Jared Vennett, Vennett
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.95,0:28:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杰瑞德·威内特，德意志银行，听着就不靠谱 - 听他说话就让人不爽\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Jared Vennett, from Deutsche, sounded very sketchy. -Sounds like a douche-bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.42,0:29:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们好啊 - 请坐\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK.. Hi.... how are you?! -Have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.69,0:29:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,来自德意志银行的杰瑞德，我们洗耳恭听了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hey mister Vennett from Deutsche Bank, who do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.72,0:29:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和多少人聊过？ - 有几个\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So, how many people have you talked to about this trade? - A few.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.53,0:29:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有意向的还不少\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}There's definitely some interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.15,0:29:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ohh..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.59,0:29:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我老板知道了非得弄死我不可\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}My boss would have my ass
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.12,0:29:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吧？杰瑞\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}are you crazy Jer?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.12,0:29:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别废话！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.70,0:29:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,滚蛋！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.43,0:29:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才打错电话给我们\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Which is why you're here talking to us on the wrong number?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.24,0:29:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听着确实感兴趣的人不少哇 - 好吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Sounds like there's a lot of interest. -Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.15,0:29:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有的人和我聊天就是看笑话寻开心 你们也不想谈正事吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A few people have us in, just to laugh at me on this deal, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.88,0:29:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也是这意思？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Is that what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.88,0:29:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是这类人，就马克爱开这种玩笑\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's not what this is, that's just how Mark is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.85,0:29:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们详细说说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Let's see what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.82,0:29:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你闻到什么东西了吗？- 什么？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm sorry, do you smell that, what is that? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.42,0:29:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么味道？ - 古龙水吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What's that smell? -Cologne?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.11,0:29:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.18,0:29:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,发财的机会！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.78,0:29:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不…钱的味道\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No... Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.90,0:29:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我闻到钱味儿了…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I smell money...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.40,0:29:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Chris....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.72,0:30:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 手脚利索点 - 抱歉\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}goddammit! -I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.32,0:30:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你们房贷证券的构成\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This is your basic mortgage bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.58,0:30:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,开始很简单\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alright, the originals were simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.94,0:30:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是几千个3A级房贷组合起来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They were just thousands of AAA-mortgages bundled together,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.72,0:30:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,政府担保\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}guaranteed by the US-government.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.68,0:30:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而现代的房贷证券就不一样了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The modern ones are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是私营的，而且由分层份额构成\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They're private. And they're made up of layers of tranches.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.19,0:30:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  份额一词来源于法语，意为某物的一部分\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} A tranche is a French word meaning "a portion of sth."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.91,0:30:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最高的3A级最先偿还\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Highest level AAA's getting paid first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.29,0:30:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最差的B级最后还，会首先断供\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The lowest rated B's getting paid last, taking on defaults first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.58,0:30:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,显然断供的B级，能要回更多的钱来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No obviously if you're buying B's you could make more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有点风险，有时候也可能偿还不了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But, they're a little risky, sometimes they fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.18,0:30:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.14,0:30:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,某处开始，有些B级或者2B级 从有点风险，变成狗屎贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Somewhere along the line, these B's and BB's went from a little risky to dogshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.06,0:30:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾桶在哪\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Where's the trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.99,0:30:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的是最低的信用评分\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm talking rock-bottom Fico-scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.87,0:30:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没有收入核实\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No Income-verification.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.81,0:30:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可调利率贷款…就是狗屎\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}adjustable rates... Dogshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.94,0:31:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,违约率已经到了1至4个百分点\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The default-rates are already up from one to four percent fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.88,0:31:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等到了8%…也肯定会到的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And if they rise to eight percent... and they will!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.16,0:31:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那这些3B级的房贷也会一钱不值\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A lot of these BBB's are going to zero too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.16,0:31:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这…别离我这么近\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And that.... You're too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.56,0:31:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是发财机会\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Is an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.19,0:31:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你说8%的警戒线，现在已经到4%了？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, You're saying that at 8 percent the bonds fail and we're already at 4 percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.28,0:31:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没错 - 到了8就是世界末日了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's right. -If they go to eight.... It's Armageddon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.29,0:31:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 那怎么没人提到过这事儿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah that's right. -How come nobody's talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.07,0:31:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你计算没问题吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And you're completely sure of the math?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.12,0:31:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看看他…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.99,0:31:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的矿工！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's my Quant!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.33,0:31:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的啥？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-Your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.40,0:31:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的量化研究员…我的数学专家！瞧瞧他！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}My quantitative... My maths specialist! Look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.62,0:31:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看到有什么与众不同的吗？看看他的脸！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You notice anything different about him? Look at his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.43,0:31:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你这也太种族歧视了…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's very racist
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他的眼睛！我提示你们一下…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look at his eyes! I'll give you a hint..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.69,0:31:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字叫做“杨”！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}His name is Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.66,0:31:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他得了国家数学竞赛的金牌…还是中国的竞赛！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He won a national maths competition.. In China!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.92,0:31:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他连英语都不会说！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He doesn't even speak English!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.65,0:31:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没错！我对数字有信心\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah! I'm sure of the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.03,0:31:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我名字叫“江”\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Actually, my name is JIANG
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.86,0:31:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会说英语\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and... I do speak English
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.85,0:32:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞德喜欢这么说，是想要让我看起来更牛逼一些\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Jared likes to say it though.. because he thinks it makes me seem more authentic
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.42,0:32:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我…其实得了数学竞赛第二名\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And... i got second in that national math competition
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.72,0:32:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你让我们做空这堆积木吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So.... You're offering us a chance to short this pile of blocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.06,0:32:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做空？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.51,0:32:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,用信用违约互换来做\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}With something called a credit default swap.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.04,0:32:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是证券的保险，不过如果证券完了 那你能拿到10倍的赔偿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's like insurance on the bond, and if it goes bust, you can make 10-to-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.20,0:32:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至有可能拿到20倍，崩溃趋势已经开始了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Even 20-to-1 return, and it's already slowly going bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.95,0:32:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,10倍，20倍，怎么可能！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}10-to-1, 20-to-1.... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.49,0:32:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也没人注意到\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And no-one is paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.23,0:32:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没人亲自去了解\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No-one is paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.79,0:32:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,银行忙着卖证券，暗地里拿提成\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Because the banks are too busy getting paid obscene fees to sell these bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.40,0:32:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等…可你就是银行的人\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But wait.... You are the bank
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.94,0:32:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你为银行工作，那你的提成也富的流油吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You work for the bank, i bet your margins are pretty nice and fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.25,0:32:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的提成和这个没关系\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Let's not talk about my margins by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.84,0:32:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我私事…好比我看你衬衫不错 问你在哪买来的女装，好玩吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Being nice and fat.... That's a nice shirt, do they make it for men?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.35,0:32:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不替银行说话？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Aren't you the bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.34,0:32:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我给银行打工\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I work for the bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.96,0:32:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我脑子没卖给银行\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't think like a bank
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.29,0:32:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大银行小银行，我赚的是钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Big banks, small bank... I like to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.70,0:32:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…让我直说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alright...Let me put it this way....
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.33,0:32:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这就像我来到失火大楼前面\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm standing in front of a burning house,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.13,0:32:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现场让你们买火灾保险\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And I'm offering you fire insurance on it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.00,0:32:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能这些证券像你说得那么差\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-How can these underlying bonds be... as bad as you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.63,0:33:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没人管吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It wouldn't be legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.84,0:33:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道里面装的什么东西\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Nobody knows what's in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.78,0:33:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道在证券里有什么鬼\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Nobody knows, what's in the bonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.57,0:33:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我见到过65%达到3A评级的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I've seen some that are 65 percent AAA-rating.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.66,0:33:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,其实95%都是次级狗屎\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That i know, for a fact, are filled with 95 percent sub-prime shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.23,0:33:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,信用评分都低于550 （FICO评分300-850，700以上认为是优）\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}With Fico's below 550
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.03,0:33:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你就吹吧！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Get the fuck out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.20,0:33:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真想被我吹晕了吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Want me to really blow your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.49,0:33:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要是市场觉得一个证券风险太高了怎么办？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}When the market deems a bond too risky to buy, what do you think we do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.40,0:33:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们猜吧！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Take a guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.82,0:33:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，才让你说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't know, you tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.34,0:33:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.28,0:33:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为像书本上说的用仓单存货抵押吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You think we just warehouse it on the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.65,0:33:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,假的，实际上我们重新打包 混上其他卖不出去的东西\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, we just repackage it, with a bunch of other shit that didn't sell
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.92,0:33:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,放到CDO里面卖\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and put it into a CDO.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.87,0:33:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- CDO？ - 对，这东西叫CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A CDO? -Yes... a CDO.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.55,0:33:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.70,0:33:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,把一些没人买的B，2B，3B级烂贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Where we take a bunch of B's, BB's and BBB's that haven't sold
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.98,0:33:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,打包成一堆…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and we put em in a pile...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.25,0:33:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,数量差不多了，就忽然叫做“分散化投资”了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and when the pile gets large enough, the whole is suddenly considered 'Diversified'.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.91,0:33:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等着…评级机构的婊子们\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and then... the whores of the rating agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.96,0:33:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,评个百分之92到93的3A级别 其他屁都不放\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Give it a 92 / 93 percent AAA-rating, no questions asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.11,0:33:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我...！你再说一遍！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Holy... what! Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.29,0:33:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,CDO，担保债务凭证\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}(CDO)Collateralized Debt Obligations
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.55,0:34:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,理解CDO很重要，CDO才是让房产危机…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's important to understand, because it's what allowed the housing crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.19,0:34:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,…祸害全国经济的关键\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}become a nationwide economic disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.49,0:34:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们的世界顶级厨师安东尼·伯尔顿解释一下\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Here's world-famous chef Anthony Bourdain to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.16,0:34:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,假设我正给一个周日下午的大餐厅备菜\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, I'm a chef on a Sunday-afternoon setting the menu of a big restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.93,0:34:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我周五定购的鱼，就好比麦克做空的房贷证券\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I ordered my fish on Friday, which is the mortgage bond that Michael Burry shorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有些鱼…没卖出去…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But... some of the fresh doesn't sell..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.43,0:34:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道原因，没准这比目鱼成精了…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't know why, maybe it just came halibut
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.20,0:34:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有海豚一样的智商\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}has the intelligence of a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.87,0:34:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我该怎么办呢？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So... what am i gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.62,0:34:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把这些3B评级的鱼扔掉吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}throw all this unsold fish, which is the BBB-level of bond, in the garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.09,0:34:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,认亏了？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and take the loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.84,0:34:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没必要！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.86,0:34:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么心灵手巧…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Being a crafty and morally honorous chef that i am...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.35,0:34:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,每种卖不掉的烂证券，我都扔到海鲜汤里去\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Every crappy levels of the bond i don't sell... i throw into a seafood stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.11,0:34:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这不再是烂鱼！这是新东西！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's not old fish! It's a whole new thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.76,0:34:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,最妙的地方就在于…卖给顾客的名头，是零售比目鱼\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The best part is.... They're eating retailed halibut!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.38,0:34:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这…就是CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That... is a CDO.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.29,0:34:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能这些东西被攒到一起\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I just need to know how these could possibly be correlated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.52,0:35:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像《爱探险的朵拉》主人公 老是第一个发现大新闻\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're like D- D- Dora the Explorering, you're the first person who has found this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.82,0:35:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等…你是说房贷证券是狗屎？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So.. hold on.. So mortgage bonds are dogshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.37,0:35:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,CDO是猫屎包起来的狗屎\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}CDO's are dogshit wrapped in catshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.88,0:35:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对，就是这个理儿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah... that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.86,0:35:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,机构们还把CDO当成国库券一样的宝贝\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Institutions treat these CDO's like they're as solid as treasury bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.44,0:35:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等着它们一钱不值吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and they're going to zero..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.84,0:35:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不对啊，去年一年就卖了5千亿的房贷证券\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, that can't be right, there, there, are 500 billion in housing bonds sold last year alone
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.15,0:35:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,信用评级机构，银行 政府也掺和在里面？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ratings agencies, the banks.... the fucking government?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.62,0:35:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你这就像在说他们闭着眼开车\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're saying they're all asleep at the wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.68,0:35:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没错！我整个部门都对这种狗屎流口水\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah! My whole department is long this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.94,0:35:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们反倒叫我胆小鸡仔\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They call me chicken little.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.63,0:35:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们叫我泡沫男孩\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They call me Bubble-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.53,0:35:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A级…废了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A's ... Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.70,0:35:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,B级废了，2B级废了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}B's.. Zero, BB's ..... Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.97,0:35:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,3B级…也是废品\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}BBB's .... Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来就是这个了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And then that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.42,0:35:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这…是啥？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What... is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.00,0:35:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是美国的房产市场\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's America's housing market.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 你说得好棒！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Thank you. - Fucking A Jared!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.88,0:35:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Shut your fucking mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.99,0:36:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 杰瑞德！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Bye Jared!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.60,0:36:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这不对劲\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.19,0:36:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定有猫腻\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He's playing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.72,0:36:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他在玩我们，他陷得太深了，拉人垫背来脱身\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He's playing us, he's got too much skin in the game, and he's dumping his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.35,0:36:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他说的是真的呢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What if he's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.07,0:36:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你当然希望他说的是真的！ - 我是希望！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You want him to be right! -Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.03,0:36:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,银行给我们信用卡的利息是25%\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The banks have given us twenty-five percent interest rates on credit cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.73,0:36:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,助学贷款也坑了大家，普通人已经没法脱身了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They have screwed us on student-loans, so we can never get out from under.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.79,0:36:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然后这家伙，走到我办公室里说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Then this guy, walks into my office and says:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.52,0:36:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这些银行太贪婪，已经忽视了市场真相了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}"Those same banks got greedy, they lost track of the market"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.38,0:36:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我还能通过他们的愚蠢赚钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And i can profit off of their stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.73,0:36:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我靠！我当然希望他是对的！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fuck! Yeah! I want him to be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.73,0:36:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能不讨厌他？ 你告诫我们注意的骗子特征他身上全有\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I mean, how come you don't hate this guy? He's everything you taught us not to trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.25,0:36:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨不起来！他这么把自己的利益摆到台面上 我倒挺尊敬他\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You can't hate him! He is so transparent in his self-interest that i kinda respect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.26,0:37:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我会从这种人手里买车吗？肯定不会\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Would i buy a car from him?... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.82,0:37:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他说的房贷市场情况是否属实？ 咱们自己去调查看看，去调查\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Is he right about the mortgage market? Let's find out. Let's find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.93,0:37:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只要回答两个简单问题\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look... It's two very simple questions:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.07,0:37:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,房地产有没有泡沫？如果有，银行了解多少？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Is there a housing bubble? And if there is... how exposed are the banks?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.23,0:37:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们赶快行动，如果情况属实\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Let's get on this quickly too, because if he is right...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.14,0:37:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那有点钱的基金都会来找我们的麻烦\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Every loser with a couple million bucks in a fund is gonna be jumping on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就出发！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.94,0:37:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根大通啊，这里可是摩根大通啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}J.P. Morgan-Chase, J.P. Morgan-Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.64,0:37:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 查理·盖勒 别废话了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Charlie Geller OK.. Don't!...Stop Saying J.P. Morgan-Chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.56,0:37:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得咱们能交好运\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I got a good feeling about this
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.19,0:37:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  杰米·希普利 就一个会面，别抱太大期望\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Jamie Shipley Just a meeting though, you know...It's just a meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.97,0:37:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,会面天天都有…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}People have meetings all the time... You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.03,0:37:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,人们喝完咖啡，就去会面…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}People drink their coffee, they have a meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.00,0:37:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 棕地基金？ - 我们在这儿！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Brownfield Funds? - Yes!  yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.21,0:37:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫克里斯，泰德交易团队的前台\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hello, Hey! Chris... I 'm on Ted's Desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.53,0:37:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫查理，查理·盖勒 我叫杰米，杰米·希普利\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm Charlie, I'm Charlie Geller, I'm Jamie, Jamie Shipley.. Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.19,0:38:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们太想在你们的交易平台上接入了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We're so excited to get setup on your trading platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.17,0:38:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊！先坐下聊一聊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Cool! Here, eh.. have a seat a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.67,0:38:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.92,0:38:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我…泰德让我…先和你们见面聊聊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So I... Ted did ask ehm.. to do us some meeting in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.03,0:38:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可我一直找不到你们的宣传资料\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}but I eh... I couldn't find any marketing material on you guys..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.41,0:38:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…我们是刚从科罗拉多州博尔德搬过来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Oh... we just moved here from Boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.85,0:38:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看看你们的招募书吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Oh, can we see some of your offering documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.91,0:38:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,其实，棕地基金用的是…我们自己的钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well Brownfield has it own... money...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.13,0:38:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我俩的存款…嗯\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's our money... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.09,0:38:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说说你们资金规模是多大？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well can you tell us how much you manage?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.14,0:38:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊！我们现在做到3千万了…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Of course! We're doing 30 million right now.... eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.41,0:38:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我们是4年前开始的 当时只有11万的本钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But we started four years ago, with a hundred-ten thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.37,0:38:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 厉害啊！- 所以你看\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Wow! -So as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.05,0:38:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的投资回报率相当厉害\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}that's pretty phenomenal returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.46,0:38:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想和摩根签署ISDA协议\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We wanna get an ISDA-agreement with J.P. Morgan,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.03,0:38:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们就能交易长线期权了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So we can deal in long-term options.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.44,0:38:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想法很好嘛！- 是啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-That's really cool! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.56,0:38:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} ISDA协议（国际掉期及衍生产品协议）\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} ISDA Agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.86,0:38:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 这个协议能够让投资者坐在“大亨”席位上\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} An agreement that lets an investor sit at the "big boy table"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 阻止愚蠢的新手扰乱高水平的交易\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} and make high level trades not available to stupid amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.20,0:38:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 押注很大的交易员，如果没有ISDA\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} Trying to be a high stakes trader without an ISDA
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.40,0:38:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 就像骑着羊驼，想要赢得超级印地赛车比赛冠军一样\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} is like trying to win the Indy 500 riding a llama.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.41,0:38:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的想法很好！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.46,0:39:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.53,0:39:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢…你们没达到ISDA的资本准入门槛\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But eh.. you guys are under the capital requirements for an ISDA.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.29,0:39:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,差多少？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}By how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.77,0:39:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…差了…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Er.. How much eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.15,0:39:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,十亿四千七百万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}One billion four-hundred-seventy millions
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.72,0:39:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.08,0:39:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还差挺多\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.12,0:39:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我们看起来挺不专业的，是吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This makes us look bad doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.57,0:39:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们连资金要求都不知道\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That we didn't know what the capital requirements were.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.68,0:39:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I..... eh..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.24,0:39:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,影响是不太积极\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's not great!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.28,0:39:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But, eh.....
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.40,0:39:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们保持这样的利润率\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Keep up those returns
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.89,0:39:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,以后发达了，记得再给我们打电话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And give us a call way down the line you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.11,0:39:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.93,0:39:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，谢谢你克里斯！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, of course! Thanks Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.70,0:39:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 祝你们好运！- 谢谢！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Have a good one guys! -Thank you Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.47,0:39:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.25,0:39:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会安排下午4点50谈正事儿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Who the fuck schedules a meeting at 4:50 in the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.54,0:39:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,美国银行和贝尔斯登没回电话也就算了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Dude, B of A and Bear didn't even return our calls
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.12,0:39:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 连美联银行这种大众货也不屌我们！ - 是啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and even fucking Wachovia blew us off! - I know man!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.01,0:39:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是其他一样在大厅里就被拍死的家伙的招股书\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Here's the prospectuses of all the other losers who didn't make it past the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.64,0:39:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不想搞这个了…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't think i can do this anymore..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.95,0:40:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计，我还年轻，还能干点正事儿！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yo, I'm young yet, i can still do something with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.09,0:40:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回科罗拉多老家 连大麻都比这边的飘\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I miss Colorado anyway. The weed's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.09,0:40:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们…请离开大厅\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Gentleman... i need you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.44,0:40:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我们马上走，咱们走\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yep, Yeah we're going, Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.94,0:40:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看这个！看看这个！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look at this, Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.85,0:40:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这人说房地产市场就是一个大泡沫！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}this guy says that the housing market is a giant bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.92,0:40:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这部分情节和真实情况有些出入\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, so this part isn't totally accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.25,0:40:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我俩不是在大厅发现了杰瑞德的推销资料\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Now, we didn't find Jared Vennett's housing bubble pitch in a lobby of a bank that rejected us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.56,0:40:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,实际情况是，一个朋友告诉了查理这件事\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Truth is... ehm.. A friend had told Charlie about it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.05,0:40:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是从金融史学家Jim Grant的个人期刊上读到的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And I read about it, in Grant’s Interest Rate Observer
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.36,0:40:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.83,0:40:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,简直像胡说的东西\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This is..... crazy stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.86,0:40:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿说房贷证券的信用违约互换\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Here, they're saying that there's 10-to-1 returns,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.20,0:40:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是10倍的收益比\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}on Credit Default Swaps for mortgage backed securities
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.93,0:40:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在房地产市场马上就要崩溃了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and the whole housing market is about to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.11,0:40:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对他俩来说，听到这消息简直像猫闻到了腥味一样\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}For Jamie and Charlie, the housing market doomsday prediction was music to their ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.97,0:40:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}bgm 《Lithium》by Polyphonic Spree\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} bgm:  Lithium by Polyphonic Spree
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.03,0:40:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他俩在杰米家的车库创业起家\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They had started working out of Jamie's garage,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.48,0:41:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,资金是杰米在东海岸倒卖帆船攒下来的11万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}with a 110 thousand Jamie had saved taking sailboats up and down the east-coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.25,0:41:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的投资策略很简单\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Our investment-strategy was simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.28,0:41:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没人愿意听到坏消息 所以人们往往低估坏事发生的概率\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}People hate to think about bad things happening so they always underestimate their likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.68,0:41:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,简单又高明的策略\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Their strategy simple and brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.72,0:41:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的对！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.91,0:41:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他俩发现，市场会低价贩卖 认为不可能发生的事情的期权\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Jamie and Charlie found: Markets will sell options very cheaply on things they think will never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.90,0:41:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样损失会很小，而一旦得利…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So, when they were wrong, they were wrong small. But when they were right.......
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.92,0:41:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就能赚很多！ -赚翻了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They were right big! - Boooooom!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.19,0:41:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 期权交易的是“买卖权利”，不需要买卖实物\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} options
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.39,0:41:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 所以需要的资金量小，可以做空\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} options
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.25,0:41:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（棕地基金） 几年间他们就把11万做到了3千万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} BROWNFIELD FUND Within a few years they had turned a 110 grand into Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.48,0:42:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  本·瑞克 沙拉…真好吃！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Ben Ricket This salad's .... Oh.. hmmm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.42,0:41:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候去纽约了…不过进展并不顺利\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Then it was time to go to New York City, And so far..... It wasn't going very well
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.56,0:41:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这个买卖可以做呢？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So what if it does seem interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.13,0:41:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，没有银行会和我们签ISDA协议\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Nope, no bank will give us our ISDA.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.35,0:41:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们没风掀不起浪啊…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We're dead in the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.58,0:41:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这类交易完全搞不起\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}These kind of trades are totally out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.19,0:41:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们必须打电话给本\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-We gotta call Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.06,0:41:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,打给他！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Call Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.27,0:41:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,本·瑞克是退下来的交易员 以前在摩根新加坡分行\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ben Ricker was a former trader in Singapore for Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.27,0:41:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,深深厌恶这一行就金盆洗手了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Quit the whole game in disgust!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.22,0:42:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,当年在科罗拉多州，本正好是杰米的邻居\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He just happened to be Jamie's neighbor when they were in Colorado
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.93,0:42:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为本在遛狗，两人才认识\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They met, walking dogs....
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.92,0:42:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不过本的世界观更阴暗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But Ben was dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.49,0:42:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不只认为金融系统会崩溃\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He didn't just think the whole system would fail
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.55,0:42:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,连全世界都会迟早毁灭\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He thought the whole world was going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.99,0:42:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了，这些都是我花园里新鲜采摘的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You know, every one of these vegetables is fresh from my garden
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.64,0:42:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们应该开一个自己的花园\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You guys should start your own garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.96,0:42:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,别用石油化工的东西污染土壤\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What you gotta do is get your soil off petrol chemicals,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.33,0:42:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,用木屑和尿来改良土壤，增加单硝酸酯\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Use wood-ash and urine, help destroy the soil, creates mononitrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.48,0:42:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,以后种子会成为硬通货！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Seeds are gonna be the new currency!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.39,0:42:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是孟山都公司的基因改造种子 我说的是原生态的健康种子\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And not those Frankenseeds from Monsanto, I'm talking about good healthy organic seeds.
