Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.86,0:49:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我的钱给我！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Give me my fucking money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.20,0:49:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你这小兔崽子\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.50,0:49:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,房产市场正处在一个小不丁点的低谷里\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The market is in an itsy-bitsy little gully right now
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.98,0:49:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好像大伙说“玩得太嗨了，咱们稍微缓缓神”\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Like everybody said: "OK, that was crazy, let's just all calm down!"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.86,0:49:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那房子刚建成的时候，我35万卖了出去\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I sold that house for 350, the year it was built.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.62,0:49:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,两年以后，就值48万，然后58万5 这是一年半以前的价格\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}two years later... 480, then 585, maybe eighteen months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.20,0:49:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这对夫妻在去年花65万买了下来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This couple bought it for 650 last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.56,0:50:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,倒霉碰上房价跌了，只能按原价卖呗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He'd let it go for that....high jump
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.40,0:50:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定觉得不值，不过会放手的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It will break his heart, but he'll let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.28,0:50:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那他为什么要卖房？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Why is he selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.96,0:50:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,夫妻俩现在都没工作\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Neither one is working right now
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.80,0:50:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,马琳，你说他们急于出手是吧？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Marlene, you'd say they're motivated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.70,0:50:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,和这片的人积极性差不多吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}As motivated as one can be in this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.82,0:50:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,左边这房子，才是真正急于出手\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This house on the left, I'd say they're properly motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.60,0:50:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我说，急于出手的也太多了点\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Wow! A lot of people seem very motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.66,0:50:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,房价小触底嘛，大伙神经过敏\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's just a gully that's all. Just nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.14,0:50:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那…我们把车停到哪儿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So... where do we stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.76,0:50:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我得和我老婆商量一下\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I need to talk to my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.62,0:50:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再等，过了这村就没这店了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}ehm.. This market won't last!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.00,0:50:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,其实，能给我介绍个房贷经纪人吗？ 你推荐的，不错的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Actually, can i talk to a mortgage broker? Anybody you recommend? Anybody you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.88,0:50:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊，是有个绝佳人选\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yes, yes, There's someone, absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.94,0:50:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这小妞肯定喜欢我啊 我帮她赚钱赚翻了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, bitch better like me, sent her ass to Cabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.06,0:50:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,连摩根士丹利都等着要我们了？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So is Morgan Stanley recruiting us? Is that..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.18,0:50:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…银行拥有我们的对冲基金\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, eh no. The bank owns our hedge-fund
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.10,0:50:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们其实不归银行管 我们主要投资金融服务公司\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We're not really a part of it, we invest in financial service companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.98,0:50:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们过来是想了解这里房贷行业的情况\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We're trying to understand the residential mortgage business.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.66,0:50:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你每个月能办多少笔贷款\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How many loans do you write each month?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.66,0:51:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没留意过，大概60笔吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't know, about 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.24,0:51:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,4年前呢？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What was it four years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.82,0:51:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,10笔…15笔的样子\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ten.... but maybe fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.60,0:51:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我是酒吧招待，现在我连船都有了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I was a bartender, now i own a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.80,0:51:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这里面有多少是可调利率的房贷？ （ 前几年低利率，然后调高）\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So, how many of these are eh.. adjustable rate Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.90,0:55:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 重新贷款:房价上涨,借房贷的人通过重新贷款 可获得最新的更低利息房贷，代价是延迟还清\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  explain refinance
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.18,0:51:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，绝大多数\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well, most.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.08,0:51:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我觉得有90%左右\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, I'd say about ninety percent
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.26,0:51:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,近几年这种房贷提成飙上天了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The bonuses on those skyrocketed a few years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.32,0:51:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们全靠这个赚钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Adjustables are bread and honey
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.76,0:51:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那房贷申请有被拒的时候吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So, do applicants ever get rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.52,0:51:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.52,0:51:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他们被拒，我就不称职了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look if they get rejected I suck at my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.50,0:51:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没钱也能贷到款？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Even if they have no money?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.36,0:51:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们公司有一种“忍者贷款”\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well, my firm offers a NINJA loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.52,0:51:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要收入和职业证明，收入一栏空着都可以\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No Income No Job Application, I just leave the income-section blank if i want.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.44,0:51:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,公司不在乎\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Corporate doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.76,0:51:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大伙想要房，公司顺应民意呗 - 你当然愿意\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}- These people just want homes, and they go with the flow. - Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.78,0:51:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们公司都不查验的吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Your companies don't verify?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.02,0:51:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我星期五下午签了房贷合同\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}If I write a loan on Friday afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.88,0:51:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大银行周一中午就会买走\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Big bank is gonna buy it by Monday lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.26,0:51:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,见怪不怪！我们也一样\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Deal! Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.44,0:52:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们能等会吗？ - 行啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Could you hold on a second? -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.88,0:52:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞不明白，为啥他们这么坦白\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't get it... Why are they confessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.74,0:52:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不是在坦白…他们这是在吹牛\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They're not confessing.... They're bragging!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.30,0:52:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,贷款的人真的知道这种贷款的风险吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Do people have any idea what they are buying?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.10,0:52:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我一般找移民\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I focus on immigrants!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.46,0:52:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等他们还不起房贷睡大街了… 你让他们签什么都愿意\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Once they find out they're getting homeless.. They'll sign where you tell em to sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.82,0:52:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不会问问题，不理解利率是什么东西\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They don't ask questions, don't understand the rates.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.60,0:52:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也找移民下手吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And you targeting on immigrants too?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.60,0:52:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,移民的信用分对他来说还太好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Their credit isn't actually bad enough for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.70,0:52:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不跟钱过不去\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look I'm a yield guy
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.20,0:52:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一笔固定利率的良性房贷，我只赚两千\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I make two thousand on a fixed rate prime
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.72,0:52:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可做一笔可调利率的次级贷，我能赚一万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But i CAN make ten thousand on a sub-prime adjustable
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.38,0:52:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的，没有脱衣舞女郎的帮忙 我也开不上宝马7系\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Trust me, I'm not driving that 7-series without strippers
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.42,0:53:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她们信用评分都不行，可是都超级有钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No-one on the pole has good credit, and they're all cash-rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.60,0:53:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像听沃伦·巴菲特说过类似的话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I think I read Warren Buffett said something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.80,0:53:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？巴菲特是谁？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What? Who's Warren Buffett?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.38,0:53:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的脱衣舞女郎…就是露肉的那种？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, So, strippers.... like exotic dancers...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.46,0:53:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,光屁股的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Nude, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.76,0:53:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,露着胸的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Topless..
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.50,0:53:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 脱衣舞女郎 - 对\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Strippers? -Yeah, Hmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.02,0:53:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能帮我们介绍个吗？ - 当然行\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Can you introduce us? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.50,0:53:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.74,0:53:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直选还贷方式多的可调房贷 我毕竟是自由职业者\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I always get option-pay adjustable. I'm a private contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.24,0:53:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,听不清，抱歉！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Can't hear you, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.54,0:53:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直选还贷方式多的那种可调房贷 我自己干，需要点灵活性\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I always get option to pay adjustable, I'm a private contractor, i need the flexibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.82,0:53:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么跟房贷公司说你的职业\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And you tell the mortgage company what you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.28,0:53:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我写的是：治疗师\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I write: Therapist
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.32,0:53:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你可以摸我！ - 一直？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You can touch me! -Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.60,0:53:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那只能在VIP房间\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Only in V.I.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.90,0:53:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不，误会了 你说你一直选可调利息房贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, no, no you say you always do adjustables
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.42,0:53:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你一套房子不止一笔贷款吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And you have more than one loan on a property?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.40,0:53:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙都这样\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Everybody does!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.76,0:53:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 至少我们这儿这样 - 我没听明白\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}At least down here -I'm sorry what?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.66,0:53:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都这样！至少我们这儿是！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Everybody does! At least down here
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.44,0:53:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样首付只要5%\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That way you'll only put down like five percent
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.44,0:53:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可房价现在不涨了，对吧？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well prices have leveled off though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.60,0:53:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，暂时不涨\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, it's a gully
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.58,0:54:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能别晃来晃去的？我照样付你钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Would you mind not moving anymore? I'll still pay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.98,0:54:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…有人盯着\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Sorry... We're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.72,0:54:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你听我说…如果房价不涨\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, look.. If home-prices don't go up,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.54,0:54:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能重新贷款了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You are not going to be able to refinance
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.78,0:54:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你就陷到房贷里脱不开身\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And you're going to be stuck paying
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.54,0:54:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等利率优惠期过了，月供涨到多少是多少\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}whatever your monthly payment is once it jumps up, whenever your teaser rate expires
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.64,0:54:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,加上逾期的利滚利，可能涨到200%到300%\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Your monthly's could go up two- to three hundred percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.68,0:54:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯说我总可以重新贷款的！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}James says i can always refinance!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.66,0:54:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那…他…就是个骗子\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well... He's ... A liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.80,0:54:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,至少对这种情况，他很可能是错的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Actually in this particular case, James probably is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.00,0:54:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,200%？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Two-hundred percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.52,0:54:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我所有房贷的？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}On all my loans?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.56,0:54:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思？不就是一套房两笔贷款吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What do you mean? We're talking about two loans on one house right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.80,0:54:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我有5套房\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I have five houses
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.96,0:54:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,外加一套公寓房\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And a condo..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.68,0:54:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有泡沫！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hey, there's a bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.34,0:54:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.46,0:54:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我，打电话给杰瑞德\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Trust me. Call Vennett,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.76,0:54:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,买上5千万房贷证券的信用违约互换\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Buy 50 million in swaps on the MBS
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.90,0:54:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,买哪个？Garabaldi 4，3B评级！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What do we got? Garabaldi IV, Triple B!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.08,0:54:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,马克，你确定吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mark, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.70,0:54:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,确定！这泡沫太扯淡了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, yeah! It's time to call bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.52,0:54:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哪些有泡沫？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Bullshit on what?
