Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.06,1:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,杰瑞德让我们追加抵押\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Vennett's asking us to post collateral
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.56,1:02:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What the hell is going on?
