Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.96,1:02:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把杰瑞德给我叫过来，这小畜生！ - 给杰瑞德打电话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Call Vennett, call that little shit! -Call Vennett!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.82,1:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让他快点滚过来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Tell him to get his ass down here
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.92,1:03:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,次级房贷断供越来越多\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So, sub-prime loans go bad,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.06,1:03:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是它们组成的房贷证券却更值钱了？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}but sub-rime bonds, which are made up of sub-prime loans, are more valuable?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.54,1:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也奇怪，他们要今天必须交齐1千9百万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I know. They want another 1.9 million by market close
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.60,1:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,信用评级机构呢？穆迪公司？标准普尔？ 他们调低了CDO或房贷证券的评级吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What about the ratings-agencies? Moody's, S&P? Are they downgrading the CDO's or mortgage bonds
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.50,1:03:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 现在评级什么样？ - 还是原封不动\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Where are the ratings of this? -They're the fucking same!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.40,1:03:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没变，还都是3A评级\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Nope, They're all still AAA!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.62,1:03:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.16,1:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在逗我？这帮混蛋，不要脸的！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Are you fucking kidding me? Those fuckers, those motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.50,1:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对外评级以后就钻到钱眼里去了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They go public and all the care about is their bottom-line and their shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.34,1:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,马克，还有事…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mark, that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.42,1:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根士丹利风险部的过来了 他们找了你老板\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The Morgan Stanley risk-guys are here -They called in Kathy Tao
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.22,1:03:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,想说服她卖掉我们的互换\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm trying to convince her to make her sell us swaps
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.44,1:03:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们觉得这些保费肯定是被套牢的买卖\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Apparently eh, tying up securing some insurance payments
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.06,1:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等着房地产崩溃是不明智的投资\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So, a housing Armageddon is not prudent investing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.98,1:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老板怎么说？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What did Kathy say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.38,1:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没表态，她一直问这是不是你的核心投资\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Nothing yet, she keeps asking if this is one of your crusades
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.32,1:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了，你走过去，语气平静，非常礼貌的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, I want you to walk back in there and very calmly, very politely
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.12,1:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,让这些风险评估师都滚蛋\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Tell the risk-assessors to fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.60,1:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后过来和我在标准普尔碰头 我们要找乔治亚聊聊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And then meet me over at Standard & Poors, we're gonna talk to Georgia
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.90,1:03:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把杰瑞德那混蛋叫过来 看我不把他脑浆打出来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Get that fuck Jared Vennett I want to bash his fucking head in
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.78,1:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…各位\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Uh, gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.62,1:04:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚和马克·鲍姆谈过了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I spoke with Mark Baum
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.28,1:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他的原话：都滚蛋\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He says: to fuck off!
