Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.04,1:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 百老汇大道25号，标准普尔评级机构\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} Standard & Poor's Ratings Agency, 25 Broadway
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.80,1:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我眼睛不好使啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't see a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.06,1:04:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我选的眼科医生总是特别忙\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Aaah, my eye-doctor is always busy
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.40,1:04:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能预约上我就得去 今天上午就这么废了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I end up taking any appointment they'll give me and then the whole morning gets shot to hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.56,1:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.10,1:04:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好咧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alrighty
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.16,1:04:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,顶尖基金的朋友们\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}FrontPoint Partners
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.18,1:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,标准普尔有什么能帮到你们的吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How can Standard & Poors help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.58,1:04:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想弄明白，为什么评级机构 不下调次级贷证券的评级\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well, we don't understand why the ratings-agencies haven't downgraded sub-prime bonds
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.70,1:04:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,证券包含的房贷，很明显情况在恶化\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}since the underlying loans are clearly deteriorating
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.66,1:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,断供率是让人们担心了 不过数字波动还在我们的合理模型之内\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well, the delinquency-rates do have people worried, but they're actually within our models
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.22,1:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.30,1:04:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你说没事就没事？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Says you?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.22,1:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你确信这些证券里的房贷是可靠的？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're convinced the underlying mortgages in these bonds are solid loans?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.22,1:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我们的观点 - 打开天窗说亮话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That is our opinion yeah. -Oh crack the tape!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.46,1:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过底层房贷的数据吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Have you looked at the loan-level data?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.58,1:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你以为我们整天在干啥 - 现在只要有信用分，就肯定能拿到房贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What you think we do here all day? They're giving these loans to anyone with a credit-score and a pulse
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.98,1:05:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,打断一下，你认为我们工作是什么？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Excuse me sir, what do you think we do here all day?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.26,1:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白，要不我们也不会过来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Not sure, I guess that's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.46,1:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.38,1:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再三反复核对过了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We can't re-recheck  and then check again!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.74,1:05:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这些房贷证券这么稳定可靠\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}If these mortgage-bonds are so stable, so solid
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.89,1:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你先检查一下你同事吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}you should check your friend
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.88,1:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Have you ever refused to rate?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.38,1:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做你的梦吧 - 我们有理由这么评级\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}that's delusional! -We stand behind it
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.48,1:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有给过这里任何一个证券 评级低于3A级别？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Have you ever refused to rate any of these bonds upper-tranches AAA?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.32,1:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能看看对应的材料吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Can we see the paperwork on those?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.60,1:05:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有义务给你们看内部信息 不管你是谁\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Oooh, I'm under no obligation to share that information with you, whoever you might be.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.02,1:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你就回答我的简单问题 给我们个去年低于3A评级的名字\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Just answer the question Georgia, can you name one time in the past year?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.30,1:05:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你去看了实际数据 最后也没有给银行想要的3A评级\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Where you checked the tape and you didn't give the banks the AAA-percentage they wanted?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.96,1:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不这么评，人家就去隔壁的穆迪评级了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}If we don't give them the ratings, they'll go to Moody's right down the block.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.96,1:05:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不配合，那我们的对头就会抢走客户的钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}If we don't work with them they will go to our competitors
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.16,1:05:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方就这么运转，我们有什么办法\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Not our fault, simply the way the world works.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.62,1:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我靠！- 明白了吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Holy shit! -Ah yes, now you see it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.12,1:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没说过！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.42,1:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就是卖信用评级的赚钱机构\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're selling ratings for fee's
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.66,1:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,信用商店\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A ratings shop
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.84,1:06:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不赚这么多钱也能维持运行啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You could afford to make less, make less.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.66,1:06:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没人这么要求我\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Nobody said that!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.62,1:06:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我能做主的，我有老板管着\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And it is not my decision, I have a boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.10,1:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在逗我？ - 我没空跟你开玩笑\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Are you kidding me? -No I am not kidding you!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.02,1:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你的立场？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Is that the angle you're taking?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.50,1:06:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这意思是只要有老板的人…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So now anybody who has a boss,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.64,1:06:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都不用为任何图财害命的勾当负责了！ 你当自己四岁小孩吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Can't be held responsible for doing shitty and illegal things! -What are you? Four?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.10,1:06:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是四岁孩子\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, eh, eh, I am not four!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.54,1:06:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是不负责！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mister Baum, I am not, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.78,1:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒奇怪，你们来找我的动机是什么\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And I wonder, I wonder, what your incentives might be.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.16,1:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是评级变了，对你们有好处啊？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Is it maybe in your best interest to have the ratings changed? Is it, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.64,1:06:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,信用违约互换你们买了多少？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How many credit default swaps do you own?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.26,1:06:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,立场和对错是两回事\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Doesn't make me wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.56,1:06:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩还装什么好人！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}just makes you a hypocrite!
