Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.08,1:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 下跌11.3% 赛恩净值\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} -11.3% SCION VALUE
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.20,1:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷断供，房贷证券却更值钱了，真见鬼了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mortgage-delinquencies went up and the CDO's got more valuable, unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.36,1:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，走势太反常了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We know, it's completely backwards!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.02,1:07:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我给贝尔斯登公司的朋友打电话 他连CDO是啥都不知道\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I just called an old friend at Bear he didn't even know what a CDO is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.14,1:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，我刚给贝尔和德意志汇过去7万块钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, I just had to wire Bear and Deutsche seventy thousand dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.68,1:07:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这感觉，就好像现在二加二等于…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's like two plus two equals...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.78,1:07:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,屎！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fish!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.68,1:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Great!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.90,1:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面显然有黑幕\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You bought into a rigged game
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.50,1:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要是钱赔光了，我就得回去家里蹲\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We lose everything.. -I'm gonna have to move back in with my mom!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.48,1:08:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想我妈管我\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}can't do that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.78,1:08:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我等会还有事儿忙\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well, alright i got a colon in a couple of mins
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.14,1:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，别挂电话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Wait a minute, hold on! Ben!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.84,1:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,本，听我说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ben, look!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.24,1:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能银行完全不懂CDO是什么东西，或者\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Either the banks are clueless and they don't know how to value these CDO's or...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.30,1:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他们想用沙子把屎盖起来，藏着掖着\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}they're suck crooks that... the CDO's are worth shit, and they're hiding it!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.32,1:08:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该再买更多！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I think we should buy more swaps!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.66,1:08:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说啥？ - 别废话，合同上白纸黑字写得清楚\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}- What? -Suck it up and pay up fellas we made a deal
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.58,1:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！不行！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No way, No!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.56,1:08:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子玩我们吗，还有脸过来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Are you fucking kidding me? you come in here you fuck up -Are you fucking seriously?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.78,1:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不不不！ - 行！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, no, no! -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.18,1:08:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你脑子烧了吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.64,1:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.88,1:08:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,建议你每年灌一次肠来排排毒\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Seriously, colonic once a year!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.28,1:08:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是个跑腿的，装逼不成等着被...吧！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ass! -You got a matching little butler-boy you butt-fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.04,1:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都发泄完了？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.12,1:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 完了… - 刚才大声骂，我都闪腰了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Think so yeah -God i pulled a muscle in my back from yelling
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.26,1:09:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷断供率一直在涨\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mortgage defaults have done nothing but go up!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.98,1:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我们房贷证券的报价还更高了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yet you quote us a higher price on the bonds
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.04,1:09:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我解释清楚！这显然不合道理\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Please explain that to me! There's no way that makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.08,1:09:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你的量化方法绝对有问题\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}There's no way you're marketing these swaps appropriately!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.84,1:09:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么理由让我们继续干？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I mean, why shouldn't we back out of this trade right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.26,1:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我说没说过，咱们谈成买卖的时候 评级机构，美国证券交易委员会\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Didn't I say, that when we made this deal, that the rating-agencies, the SEC
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.84,1:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大银行们全都不懂？说没说过？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and the big banks were clueless! Didn't I say that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.86,1:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 说过没有？ - 有说过的，有说过的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Didn't I say it? -Yes you did, you did!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.72,1:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.28,1:09:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们脚都开始着火了，心里却想着牛排应该烤熟了 你还觉得奇怪？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}now their foot's on fire and they think their steak is done, and you're surprised?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.40,1:09:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是愚蠢，这是诈骗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's not stupidity... that's fraud!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.28,1:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我说清楚愚蠢和违法的区别 我就去把我小舅子抓起来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Tell me the difference between stupid and illegal and I'll have my wife's brother arrested.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.12,1:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 挺好笑的！ - 你们还是没弄明白整个系统有多蠢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That was funny! -I guess you just don't realize how clueless the system really is!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.64,1:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认，是有一些见不得人的勾当\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yes, there's some shady shit going down!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.02,1:09:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但相信我，这是愚蠢驱使的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}but trust me, it's fueled by stupidity!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.80,1:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你们这些人\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look at yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.72,1:09:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,都觉得自己是敢于怀疑的人\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You know you passed yourselves off as cynical people but....
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.32,1:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可你们还对这帮青天大老爷抱有希望？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You still have some faith in the system don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.82,1:10:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不抱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.06,1:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,文尼是明白人！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well, except for Vinnie!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.10,1:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在乎？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Who gives a shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.98,1:10:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行！- 听我说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No way! -Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.98,1:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要么我们对，要么我们错得离谱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Either we're right, or we're wrong in a giant, giant way!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.32,1:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真错了，得找高人给我们点醒才行\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And if we're wrong then we gotta find someone to help us get out of this trade
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.98,1:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在是一点都不觉得我们占理\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm not feeling remotely confident that we're right
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.50,1:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,万一咱们错了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And, and... If we're wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.06,1:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来告诉我们？有谁懂？没人懂！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Who's gonna tell us? Who understands this stuff? It makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.06,1:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该去拉斯维加斯！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I think we need to go to Vegas!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.86,1:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那儿有什么？ - 去哪儿干啥\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What's in Vegas? -Vegas!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.20,1:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯维加斯又能有什么东西？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What the hell is in Las Vegas?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.20,1:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下周那里召开美国证券化论坛年会\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The American Securitization Forum is there next week
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.52,1:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每个证券、CDO、次级贷、倒卖交换的交易员都会去\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Every bond and CDO-salesman, sub-prime lender and swap-trader is gonna be there
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.22,1:10:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我这么说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm telling you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.40,1:10:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你挣的是他们手里的钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Your bet is against their money,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.98,1:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候去看看人傻钱多是怎么回事了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}it's about time you find out just how dumb that money really is
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.90,1:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不喜欢拉斯维加斯\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}God no, I hate Vegas!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.14,1:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,听说吃的东西特别好，那里也有松久寿司店了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I hear the food has gotten really good in Vegas, they have a Nobu now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.86,1:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不惦记着吃吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}could you fucking stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.04,1:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 美国证券化论坛，拉斯维加斯\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} American Securitization Forum, Las Vegas
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.24,1:11:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}bgm:《The Phantom of the Opera》by Andrew Webber\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} bgm: THE Phantom of the Opera, by Andrew Lloyd Webber
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.24,1:11:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 汽车抵押贷款 工资日贷款\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} Auto Title Loans & Payday Loans
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.04,1:11:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 凯撒宫酒店\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Caesars Palace
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.04,1:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 择一抵押公司CEO保罗·丹顿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Option One CEO Paul Dantone
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.34,1:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8} 房贷市场仍然稳健，后劲十足\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  The Mortgage Market is Strong & Getting Stronger
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.02,1:11:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,证券“贵”的意思是？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}... in a sense? -If the bond is "rich", it is...?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.28,1:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只说明证券定价过高\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}that just means it's overpriced
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.28,1:11:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 飞机上睡不着我就自己准备了一下 - 咱们集中精神！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I can't sleep on a plane so I did my homework -OK, let's focus!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.58,1:11:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是为了什么来的？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What's our goal?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.20,1:11:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,搞清楚这买卖是千载难逢的机会\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Figure out if this is a deal of a lifetime or...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.68,1:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还是别人比我们懂得都多 咱们回头会亏大发了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}everyone knows here something we don't and we're gonna get royally screwed
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.20,1:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和贝尔公司的人接触的时候 注意你们的目的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Right, remember that when you meet with guys from Bear!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.12,1:12:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你们安排见面机会\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'll set you up with a face-to-face
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.92,1:12:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，地方在哪？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Awesome, where is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.36,1:12:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天！5年前这年会还是穷鬼聚会\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Holy shit! Five years ago Securitization was a loser-convention
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.88,1:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也就有100到200人出席\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}a hundred, maybe two-hundred people would show
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.08,1:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,产业每年五千亿的发展之后，就变成这样了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}500 billion dollars a year later you get this!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.10,1:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这里自带装逼表情的人还真多\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}There's a lot of smug-looking people in here huh!?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.78,1:12:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好像暴发户白人都跑来了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It looks like someone just hit a pinata that was filled with white people who suck at golf
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.68,1:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都从哪儿冒出来的？ - 别抱怨了，肯定很好玩\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I mean, who are all these clown? -Ah come on, I think it looks fun!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.44,1:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，杰瑞德说咱们赚的是这些人的钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Charlie, Vennett says these are the people we're betting against.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.02,1:12:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们过去，克里斯，到我左边去，别挡道\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, here we go Chris on my left, Chris, on my left!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.64,1:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大家好 - 什么时候能见到你说的那些爱心天使\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Gentlemen! -When do we get a chance to face-time with some of these lovely folks?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.04,1:12:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯，把门卡发给他们\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Chris, give em the key cards!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.60,1:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别弄混了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Do you even know which key-cords you're giving out?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.00,1:12:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生们路上还顺利吗？ - 没什么事儿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}First of all, how was your travel? -Uneventful?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.84,1:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事 - 我来了6小时了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Uneventful! -OK, I've been here for six hours!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.26,1:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经锻炼完，吃了两个荷包蛋 还和演员斯坦顿一起打牌\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I've already been to the Gym, I had two poached eggs, and I played blackjack with Harry Dean Stanton
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.10,1:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你记日记还真清楚\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Thank you for your diary!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.94,1:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想找人见面聊 - 提醒你们记住，我们是来收集信息的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Face-time! I'd like some face-time! -Just remember, we're here just to gather information!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.14,1:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是收集信息，不要打草惊蛇\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We're gathering information, we're not advertising our short-position!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.78,1:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,别吓到大伙儿，行不行？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Right? We don't want to spook anybody! Can we do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.96,1:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你说话太直，还老是不停嘴\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You got a big mouth, and you like to run it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.48,1:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这几天能不能收敛一点？ - 好吧，好吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Can you just keep it shut for a few days? -OK, OK!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.38,1:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心，我们会好好套话的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, don't worry, we'll play nice!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.18,1:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.92,1:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,商业形势大好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Business is good!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.20,1:13:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,利润也很高！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Profits are strong!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.58,1:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷还坚持着经济的中流砥柱作用\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and the mortgage continues to be the bedrock on which this economy is built.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.74,1:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去年我们在次级贷市场有些损失\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yes, we had to take some losses in our sub-prime department last year,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.48,1:13:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不过预计也就最多损失5%\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But those losses, will be contained at only five percent!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.40,1:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.38,1:13:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们住宅业务板块的表现\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}In our residential sector...
