Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.76,1:20:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,连马克和麦克都没有做空2A\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Not even Baum or Berry thought to short the Double-A's
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.74,1:20:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们做了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.06,1:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这个小不点屎洞基金\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Little Brown Hole Capital
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.16,1:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想做空一些2A级的CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So we're interesting in shorting some of the AA-tranches of CDO's
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.10,1:21:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,直说吧，你俩在打什么主意？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Come on guys, what's the angle?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.88,1:21:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没其他意思，新手嘛，很想拿这个试手！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I've got no angle, we're new to this, we're just so hyped!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.18,1:21:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想买1千5百万互换，做空2A级\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We wanna do fifteen million in swaps on the Double-A tranche
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.68,1:21:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是搞不懂你们\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.74,1:21:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩愿意买多少就买多少\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You can buy as much Double-A tranches as you want!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.32,1:21:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那就4千万做空2A吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Forty million against the Double-A
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.70,1:21:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哥们，你愿意买多少我都卖给你\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Brother, I would sell you as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.24,1:21:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我在买啥，你想卖吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I understand perfectly Bob! Want the deal?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.74,1:21:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，我没问题\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's cool, that's alright with me!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.58,1:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.00,1:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样，快停下来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}don't do that! Stop, Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.96,1:21:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别闹了！查理！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Stop that! -Charlie! Wooooh!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.68,1:21:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来，你俩！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Stop it, Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.62,1:21:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.20,1:21:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你们刚刚做了什么事吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Do you have any idea what you just did?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.44,1:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我俩做成了一辈子一遇的买卖啊，应该庆祝\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Come on, we just made the deal of our lifetime, we should celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.06,1:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩在赌未来美国经济崩溃\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You just bet against the American economy!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.02,1:21:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊！没错！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fuck yeah we did! -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.40,1:22:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这意味着 - 太棒了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Which means! Fuck yeah! OH!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.58,1:22:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着，如果我们赌对了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Which means... If we're right....
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.46,1:22:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们是对的，人们会无家可归\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}If we're right, people lose homes!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.30,1:22:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大批人会失业\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}people lose jobs!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.84,1:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大家没了退休存款，养老钱都没了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}People lose retirement savings, people lose pensions!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.06,1:22:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我最讨厌这行的就是这一点 人不是数字！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You know what i hate about fucking banking! It reduces people to numbers!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.48,1:22:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那我告诉你，失业率上升1%\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Here's a number! Every one percent unemployment goes up,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.44,1:22:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡人数会增加4万人，明白吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}40 thousand people die! Did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.44,1:22:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 知不知道？ - 不，我们不了解\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Did you know that? -No, I didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.50,1:22:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是有点兴奋\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We were just excited!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.34,1:22:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还跳舞就太过分了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Just don't fucking dance!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.28,1:22:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你要去哪\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alright! -Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.40,1:22:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我心里有点发毛了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Whoah, I just got really scared!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.16,1:22:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今天表现挺好嘛\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}First of all, great show today!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.14,1:22:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,简直好极了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You were terrific!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.08,1:22:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 你嘴不严实还真是我出乎意料\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Thank you! -Your big mouth was a revelation!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.46,1:22:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,理解万岁\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I appreciate that!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.22,1:22:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们担心有人暗箱操作？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You worried you, and your swaps were getting played?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.88,1:22:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这个机会，让你们去看看对手是谁\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well, this is an opportunity for you to meet who you're betting against!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.38,1:22:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,别觉得自己正义，就不听不进他的话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Try not to get too righteous and listen a little!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.14,1:22:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，这人是谁？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, Fine! Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.70,1:22:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,24K级的混蛋\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A real solid-gold asshole!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.64,1:22:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我是CDO经理\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm a CDO-manager
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.98,1:22:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有这个职位？ - 在哈丁顾问公司就有\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A CDO-manager? -Yup, at Harding Advisors
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.96,1:23:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没想过CDO还有什么要管的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I didn't realize that there was anything to manage with CDO's
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.80,1:23:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不奇怪\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.78,1:23:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们筛选进入CDO投资组合的证券 监控背后的资产情况\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We select the securities that go into the CDO-portfolio and monitor the assets
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.66,1:23:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我主要做美林证券的CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I do most of Merrill-Lynch's CDO's
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.52,1:23:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是代表投资人还是美林？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Do you represent the investors or Meryll-Lynch?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.72,1:23:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,投资人啊！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The investors!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.70,1:23:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You do.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.02,1:23:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah! -But...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.60,1:23:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,美林不可能白白送客户给你\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Meryll-Lynch isn't gonna send you any customer unless you put
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.32,1:23:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你把美林也包含进CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Merrill-Lynch's bonds in your CDO....
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.12,1:23:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,问得好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Good question!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.98,1:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以假设…美林和我\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Let's just assume Merrill and I have a...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.58,1:23:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们关系不错\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}we have a good relationship
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.60,1:23:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你和美林证券关系不错？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You have a good relationship with Merrill-Lynch?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.94,1:23:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起做买卖\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We've been doing business together
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.10,1:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你选出的CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And so the CDO's..
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.06,1:23:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这些CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}that you create
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.26,1:23:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都是最高品质的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}are, are, are, of the highest quality
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.16,1:23:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,最有价值的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and the highest of value!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.02,1:23:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是当然 - 那是当然…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Absolutely! -Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.32,1:23:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不担心正在上升的断供率吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Are you at all concerned about the rising default-rates?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.84,1:23:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我个人不觉得CDO有风险\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I assume no risk for this produce myself Mark
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.56,1:23:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.52,1:23:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那我直说吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So let me get this straight
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.88,1:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,银行联系你\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The bank calls you up
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.22,1:24:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,让你帮忙卖他们的证券\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They give you the bonds they wanna sell
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.76,1:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再送给你客户，给你钱让你运行公司\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They give you clients, they give you money to run your business,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.70,1:24:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,提成也少不了你的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Give you fat fee's for doing so
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.54,1:24:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然还代表投资者？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}but you represent the investors?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.96,1:24:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是这个逻辑吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.94,1:24:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.28,1:24:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不在美林大厦里工作\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But we're not in the Merrill-Lynch building!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.96,1:24:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你在哪 - 我在新泽西\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}OK, where are you? -We're in New Jersey!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.90,1:24:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,开车20分钟就到了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're twenty minutes away!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.56,1:24:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,5分钟就行了，如果你坐直升飞机\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Five, if you use the helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.32,1:24:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好玩吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's funny eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.74,1:24:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好玩\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.02,1:24:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Oh boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.60,1:24:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你老板要发作了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Your boss is about to explode!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.92,1:24:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他太想搞明白了，发作不了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, he's too curious to explode!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.74,1:24:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，你再解释一下\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hold on, say that again!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.06,1:24:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,两个CDO，A包含着B的一部分\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}CDO A, has parts of CDO B
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.46,1:24:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后B也包含A一部分，然后AB被放到C里面\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And CDO B, has parts of CDO A and then they both get put inside CDO C.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.76,1:24:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对，这就是CDO平方\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah and that one is called CDO square!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.62,1:24:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,CDO的CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A CDO of a CDO!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.22,1:24:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,明白？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.22,1:24:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,CDO还能包含你互换押注剩下的部分\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And then there's CDO's made up of the opposite sides of the bet you made with the swaps
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.10,1:24:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们叫它，合成CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We call them, synthetic CDO's
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.28,1:24:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你说啥？合成CDO？真是乱套了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What did you just say? Synthetic CDO's? That is fucking crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.40,1:24:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没有乱，这很赚钱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's not! It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.70,1:25:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他脸都气红了，像枪战游戏里的坏蛋\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}His face is starting to boil He looks like the bad guy from DOOM
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.18,1:25:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们假设\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alright, let's say...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.54,1:25:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你有5千万美元的次级贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You have a pool of 50 million in sub-prime loans
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.24,1:25:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那赌在上面的钱，能有多少？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How much money could be out there betting on it
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.40,1:25:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的合成CDO和互换里？就按今晚的行情\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}In your synthetic CDO's and swaps? right now! Tonight!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.74,1:25:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,5千万的次级贷…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}50 million.. hmm..
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.04,1:25:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,10亿美元吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}a billion dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.36,1:25:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.30,1:25:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果麦克最早发现的房贷证券是火柴的话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}If the mortgage-bonds that Michael Burry discovered were the match...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.94,1:25:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,房贷市场衍生出的证券规模有多大\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How much bigger is the market for insuring mortgage bonds than for actual mortgages?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.20,1:25:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大概20倍吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}About twenty times!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.46,1:25:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果房贷证券是火柴\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}If the mortgage bonds were the match...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.74,1:25:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那CDO就是煤油弄湿的破布\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Then the CDO's were the kerosene soaked rags.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.32,1:25:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而合成CDO，就是原子弹\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Then the synthetic CDO was the atomic bomb
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.92,1:25:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,启动按钮被一个酒鬼总统把持着\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}with a drunk president holding his finger over the button
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.68,1:25:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时刻，在这破餐馆\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It was at that moment in that dumb restaurant
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.04,1:25:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,马克表情像傻了一样 他头一次意识到\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}with that stupid look on his face that Mark Baum realized
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.22,1:25:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,整个世界经济可能要崩溃了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The whole world economy might collapse!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.24,1:26:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们在想什么\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And i know what you're thinking!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.40,1:26:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,合成CDO又是什么鬼\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What the fuck is a synthetic CDO?
