Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.22,1:40:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我听着呢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Listening!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.78,1:40:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 贝利博士？ - 是我\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Dr. Burry? -Yah!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.60,1:40:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高盛的迪伯·温斯顿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Deeb Winston, Goldman Sachs
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.98,1:40:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了一下你的价位\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Listen, I've been reviewing your position
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.40,1:40:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想要和你讨论估值的情况，尽可能的公平\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I wanted to discuss your marks, make sure they're fair!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.64,1:40:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想…你的意思是\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, I, I, I thi, I think you mean.. That you've..
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.94,1:41:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经做空了自己的仓位 这样你总算能认真评估我的互换了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}secured a net-short position yourselves, so you're free to mark my swaps accurately for once
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.52,1:41:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在对你们也有利\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Because it's now in your interest to do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.40,1:41:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我不知道你要我怎么说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ehm... I'm not sure what you want me to say
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.66,1:41:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I think that....
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.66,1:41:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你该说的都说了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I think you've already said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.50,1:41:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉高盛的杰夫，我绝对不会转移基金 太扯淡了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You tell Jeff at Goldman that I'm not transferring funds, this is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.70,1:41:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,回头再说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Okay, we'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.86,1:41:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}thank you...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.64,1:41:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么快就过来了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Thanks for coming so quickly Mark -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.36,1:41:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你听说了摩根有一些损失\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I know you've been hearing rumblings about some losses Morgan has suffered.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.26,1:41:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恭喜你 - 恭喜什么？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-Congratulations On what?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.06,1:41:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.76,1:41:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  吸奶器，凯茜已经怀孕了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Breast pump, indicating pregnant
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.70,1:41:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.62,1:41:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉挺好的吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ehm.. -Having fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.52,1:41:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还行！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yes!  He he!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.26,1:41:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是感觉不错\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Tons!, Ehm....
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.02,1:42:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想告诉你\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I just wanted you to know that ehm...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.06,1:42:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根是遭受了一些损失 但我们的流动资产还是很稳健\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yes, Morgan has suffered some losses, but our liquidity is strong,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.26,1:42:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要再担心什么了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And there's no cause for concern!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.64,1:42:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那需要担心本尼吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Would Bennie Kreeger be concerned?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.90,1:42:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,听人说他损失惨重\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Because word on the street is he took some pretty heavy losses
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.42,1:42:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜，别遮掩了，咱们都认识多少年了…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Kathy come on, we know each-other.. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.16,1:42:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧…情况有多严重\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How..how..how bad is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.54,1:42:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ok...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.62,1:42:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在两年以前，摩根证券部门的克里格 也开始做空次级贷\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Two years ago, Bennie Kreeger in Morgan's bond-department also started shorting sub-prime housing
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.92,1:42:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 20亿做空3B级 - 本尼比我想的还要聪明啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Two billion in Triple-B's -Benny is smarter than i thought!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.58,1:42:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不，他一点也不聪明\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, he's not smart at all!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.14,1:42:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,交的保费搭进去了其他利润\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The premiums on the swaps ate into his desks profit
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.66,1:42:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保住3B的做空\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}To cover his Triple-B shorts,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.62,1:42:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他卖了很多的A和2A的交换做保护，很多！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He sold a lot of A- and Double-A swaps as protection, A lot!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.12,1:42:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得，不可能A级的也会受影响\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}He believed that there was no way, that they could be affected.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.82,1:42:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会说是摩根士丹利卖给我们交换的吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Tell me Morgan-Stanley doesn't hold the contracts on these swaps
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.24,1:42:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Holy shit
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.50,1:42:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在找我们的对家是谁\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}All this time I've been trying to figure out whom I've been betting against.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.24,1:43:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到是我们的母公司\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And it's Morgan-Stanley
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.78,1:43:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,遭殃的是自己的公司\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Which is me....
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.14,1:43:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,风险敞口有多少？30亿？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What's your exposure? Three billion?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.48,1:43:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能超过40亿吧？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Please don't tell me it's more than four!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.32,1:43:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能回答你这问题\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I can't answer that!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.98,1:43:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以说…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yes you can answer that, because...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.22,1:43:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我过来的时候，看到走廊上的人都在哭\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I walk in here and people are crying in your hallway
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.08,1:43:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Kathy..
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.56,1:43:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我说什么事儿都好 可什么事儿现在都不好！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You bring me in to tell me everything is fine, and everything is not fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.32,1:43:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟现在是怎么了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What? What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.32,1:43:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,做多的敞口有…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Long exposure is...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.46,1:43:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,150亿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}fifteen billion
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.34,1:43:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的老天爷，你在开玩笑吧！ - 你总是说断供率不可能超过8%的！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Jesus Christ, are you fucking kidding me?! -You kept saying defaults over eight percent were impossible!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.74,1:43:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那样会有1百万人无家可归 - 我的天\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}-That there would be a million homeless Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.26,1:43:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根和我们没有关系\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, but we have nothing to do with Morgan-Stanley
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.86,1:43:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那你上破产法庭这么说去\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah... Just tell the bankruptcy-court
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.28,1:43:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根破产，我们所有的钱都会转到 他们的资产负债表上\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Morgan fails, all our accounts go on their balance sheet
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.74,1:44:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太疯狂了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.80,1:44:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根输了烂赌注，却让我们来还账？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Morgan makes a sucker's bet and we pay their fucking gambling debt?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.88,1:44:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做空摩根的股票！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Short the bank's stocks! -Wait..
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.46,1:44:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,或者等市场一开始交易，就卖了我们的互换\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Or we sell our swaps, when the market opens
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.28,1:44:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拿到奖金，我们的投资人拿到收益\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We get our bonuses, our investors get their profit
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.82,1:44:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们能拿到一块钱里的三毛钱 至少能保命\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We get... thirty cents on the dollar, Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.02,1:44:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们比这值3倍\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We're three times that
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.66,1:44:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要是买家市场都没了，就烂到手里了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Not if there's no market up to sell them in
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.44,1:44:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，我不能把救生船送给这些人\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Forget it, I'm not giving any lifeboats
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.52,1:44:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,马克，如果摩根垮了，到头来我们什么都没有了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mark, if Morgan goes under, we end up with nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.94,1:44:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,文尼\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Vinnie...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.56,1:44:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别争了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Jesus, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.42,1:44:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我说卖，咱们再卖\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I say, when we sell
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.10,1:44:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你跟华尔街有私人恩怨\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look I get that this is personal for you,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.66,1:44:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是我们对投资人也要负责 - 我们不需要负责\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But we have a fiduciary responsibility -No, no we don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.70,1:44:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们负责？这里谁给别人负责？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Respons..? Nobody is acting responsible!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.04,1:44:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,责任！跟我谈负责\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fuck responsibility! Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.48,1:44:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大银行的那些混蛋们，回头能…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The assholes at the big banks, are gonna take..
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.38,1:44:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们点菜吗？ - 我们在说正经事…别打扰\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You boys want menu's now? -We're talking!.. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.00,1:44:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.64,1:45:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要等着，耐心等着\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We are going to wait, and we are going to wait
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.86,1:45:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等到他们知道疼了，开始流血了才行\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We are going to wait, until they feel the pain, until they start to bleed
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.58,1:45:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是我想要的结果\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That is what I want
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.52,1:45:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们的客户怎么办 我们在拿他们的钱冒风险\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, but what about our clients, they've been trusting us with their savings.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.86,1:45:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我说卖，我们再出手\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I say when we sell!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.20,1:45:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你公报私仇的时候\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This isn't about you!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.52,1:45:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我说卖，再出手！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hey, hey, HEY! I say when we sell!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.78,1:45:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，那听你的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Whatever you say Mark
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.14,1:45:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计你看新闻了吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Dude, did you hear the news?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.82,1:45:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,两个贝尔投资的房贷对冲基金爆仓了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ok, so not only did two mortgage hedge-funds backed by Bear-Stearns go belly-up
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.10,1:45:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且现在贝尔还被集体诉讼\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}but now, there's a class-action lawsuit against Bear
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.64,1:45:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,坏了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.62,1:45:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我做！用力！用力！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Let's go! Push, Push!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.30,1:45:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那怎么了？贝尔会破产吗？ - 我们不能冒这个险\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So? What? Bear could really collapse here? -That's a risk we really shouldn't take!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.22,1:45:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有80%的互换，是从贝尔那里买的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But eighty percent of our swaps is Bear
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.88,1:45:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能陪个精光\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.14,1:45:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生！- 马上就好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hey Sir! -One second!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.86,1:45:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是我的看法 - 我们买了这东西，却不知道怎么卖\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's my opinion! -Aw, we bought these fucking things, and we have no clue how to sell them
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.54,1:45:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，所以我们得找本帮忙\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I know, we have to get Ben to do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.06,1:46:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直给他打电话，他也不回\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I've been trying to call him, but he won't get back to me
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.82,1:46:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他和老婆一家人在度假，在英国！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, he's on vacation with his wife's family! They're in England!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.34,1:46:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.42,1:46:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  黑马酒吧，英国南部港口艾克斯茅斯\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  The Black Horse Pub, Exmouth England
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.02,1:46:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（本：现在出手还太早）\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  too soon for that
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.28,1:46:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,本，你能听清吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hello, Ben? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.34,1:46:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们好 - 我们在，你能听清吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Guys? -Yeah, we're here, can you hear us?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.56,1:46:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我听的清楚\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Guys?- We hear ya, Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.18,1:46:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里电话和网络信号都不好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I probably got cell-phone and WiFi-service
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.24,1:46:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要这样卖掉2亿的证券\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm trying to sell 200 million dollars worth of securities
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.16,1:46:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这酒吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}In a pub...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.64,1:46:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,闻着绵羊味儿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}smells like sheep
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.92,1:46:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你能行的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.80,1:46:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想给你压力 但你搞不定的话，我们就全赔光了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't want to pressure you Ben, but if you don't pull this off, we lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.08,1:46:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,看看瑞士瑞信银行的胃口如何\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ok, let's see what Credit Suisse's appetite is.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.48,1:46:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是棕地基金，我想要抛售我的信用违约互换\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This is Brownfield Fund, I'm wanting to unload my credit default swaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.00,1:46:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，你们有多少\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alright, what've you got?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.62,1:46:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有20个2A级别的CDO\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Twenty Double-A tranches of CDO's
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.92,1:46:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…这些现在行情不太好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Eh yes.. but these eh... these are pretty bad
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.36,1:46:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，全是垃圾\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Absolutely, they're complete shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.76,1:46:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的… - 面值是2亿50万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What's your.. what's your? - Face-value is 205 million
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.06,1:46:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,美元\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.30,1:47:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们能…以40收购\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alright, we could, we could go to forty
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.94,1:47:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，至少要1亿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, we want at least a hundred million
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.26,1:47:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,1个亿？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}A hundred million?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.88,1:47:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是毒品贩子，还是搞银行的？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Who are you a drug-dealer or a banker?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.16,1:47:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是银行家，就立马给我滚蛋\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Cause if you're a banker you can fuck right off!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.76,1:47:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道能不能坐庄，直接说你的最好报价\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I don't know if we can make a market, just give me your best price!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.06,1:47:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦！1个亿还嫌不够\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, Check! a hundred million worth, and aim higher!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.82,1:47:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们期望差太多\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I think we're far apart
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.58,1:47:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是不想买，就直接挂断\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Look if you don't want to deal, just hang up.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.52,1:47:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我料想的一样\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.80,1:47:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,9千万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ninety million
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.94,1:47:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,7千万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Seventy!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.16,1:47:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,8千5百万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Eighty-five
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.98,1:47:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 7千8百万 - 8千4百万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Seventy-eight -Eighty-four!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.84,1:47:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 7千8百万 - 8千4百万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Seventy-eight -Eighty-four!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.96,1:47:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是贝利博士\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's Dr. Burry
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.70,1:47:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}看来金融危机马上来了 （ 全国断供率超过12%）\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Looks like the collapse of the financial sector is imminent ( national default rates above 12 percent)
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.62,1:47:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我以现在的仓位出手\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Start to sell my position
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.88,1:47:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,23亿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}2.3 billion
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.12,1:47:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，我可以等着\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Sure, I'll hold!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.06,1:47:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  亲爱的劳伦斯\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Dear Lawrence
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.26,1:47:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  你在赛恩资本的总盈利为4.89亿\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Your profits totaling 489 million from Scion Capital
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.20,1:48:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  已经转存到你的账户了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  have been deposited into your account
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.20,1:48:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  不用谢。\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.50,1:48:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  德意志银行纽约分行, 4千7百万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} Deutsche bank new york. 47 million
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.88,1:48:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最终我还是对的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So I was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.22,1:48:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我被人喷了两年…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I took a rash of shit for two years. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.12,1:48:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我是对的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I was right! And...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.54,1:48:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都错了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Everyone was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.00,1:48:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我还拿到了奖金支票\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And yeah i got a bonus-cheque for it
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.10,1:48:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来告我啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Sue me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.78,1:48:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,随便了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.48,1:48:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这钱是不少，我能感到你们心里有看法\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's a lot of money! I get it, I can feel you judging me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.98,1:48:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显嘛\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's palpable
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.02,1:48:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可是呢\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.86,1:48:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没说过我是这个故事里的英雄人物\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I never said I was the hero of this story
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.72,1:48:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Hey, hey babe!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.18,1:48:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,情况怎么样？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How are we looking?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.42,1:48:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,…八…万\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}...ace... goi..
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.72,1:48:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}S-Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.14,1:48:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是8千万 - 8千万成交了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, eighty million! -Ok, so eighty million!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.36,1:48:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,8千万，8千万，这挺好的是吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Eighty million, eigthy million, that's good right?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.50,1:48:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,8千万很好，谢谢你，非常感谢！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Eighty is great, eighty is great, thank you, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.36,1:48:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,钱都汇到瑞士联合银行了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Most of them went to UBS
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.28,1:48:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们运气相当不错\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're very lucky!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.74,1:49:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天法国把国内最大的货币市场账户冻结了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The largest bank in France froze it's customer's money-market accounts today
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.40,1:49:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,风暴已经传到欧洲了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This thing is hitting Europe!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.04,1:49:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,希腊和爱尔兰已经完了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Greece and Iceland are finished
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.00,1:49:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,西班牙正在遭殃\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Spain is teetering
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.34,1:49:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的？这么严重\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Are you serious? Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.28,1:49:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,本，等你回家给我们打电话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Ben call us when you get home!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.18,1:49:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过放电话之前请等一下\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But hey, before you go... I'm just wondering...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.40,1:49:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想问…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Uhm..
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.90,1:49:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要和我们做这件事\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Why did you do this with us?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.16,1:49:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你并不需要…当然我们很感谢你…但\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You didn't have to, and eh.. you know, thank you, but, eh....
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.12,1:49:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.68,1:49:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们说想要发财，现在你们有钱了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You guys said you wanted to get rich! -Now you're rich!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.06,1:49:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  2008年3月14日\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  2008 March 14
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.14,1:49:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,房产和银行还在持续出血 只有一家大单做空的还拒绝出售\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}As the housing-markets and banks continues to hemorrhage, only one of the big shorts refused to sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.96,1:49:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}马克·鲍姆的空头（演讲人 格林·斯潘）\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} Keynote Speaker Alan Greenspan Mark Baum
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.84,1:49:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这简直比咱们导演的还要好 他在会议上和布鲁斯·米勒同台讨论\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So it was beyond perfect, when he was asked to speak at a conference opposite Bruce Miller
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.80,1:49:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,著名的乐观投资人\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Famous bullish investor
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.68,1:49:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他和马克辩论以后\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}After he and Mark had their debate
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.12,1:50:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,格林斯潘，整个金融危机的总设计师 还要继续讲话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Alan Greenspan, one of the architects of the whole crisis, was scheduled to speak
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.72,1:50:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,马克办公室的人都来了 把朋友也邀请过来了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Everyone in Mark's office showed up, even invited friends!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.74,1:50:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这就像金融界的阿里和福尔曼的拳击世纪对决\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This... was the Ali versus Foreman of the financial world
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.46,1:50:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,现实主义者对战傻瓜\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Realists versus the fools
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.92,1:50:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们以为事情不可能更完美的时候 你敢相信…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And if it seems almost too perfect... trust me!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.46,1:50:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这事儿发生了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This happened!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.54,1:50:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家的光临\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Welcome everyone!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.72,1:50:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  贝尔股价 47\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Bear at 47
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.00,1:50:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我们热烈欢迎\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Please... Give a generous welcome to...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.40,1:50:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯·米勒和马克·鲍姆\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mister Bruce Miller.... and Mark Baum
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.92,1:50:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,系好安全带看戏了！\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Strap yourself in!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.70,1:50:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有些人可能知道 贝尔斯登刚刚接受了一笔摩根的贷款\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So as some of you may know, Bear-Stearns has just received a loan from J.P. Morgan
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.60,1:50:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,当然我们等些时间才能看到市场的反馈\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Of course we gonna have to wait to see how the markets react
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.52,1:50:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但这事本身就能打消对贝尔银行的担心了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But that should lay to rest any concerns about the bank self!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.36,1:51:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解，所以你本人不会出售你的2亿股票了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, I take it, you have no plans to sell your two-hundred million in Bear stock
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.42,1:51:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不，实际上等我们聊完 我还要再买进更多\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}No, as a matter of fact, when we're done here, I'll probably go buy some more!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.38,1:51:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而对立观点…马克·鲍姆\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}For the opposing view... Mister Baum
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.34,1:51:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我得站起来说\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I gotta stand for this
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.20,1:51:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，大家好\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Okay, Hi!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.06,1:51:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们公司投资理念很简单\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}My firm's thesis is pretty simple
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.90,1:51:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,华尔街把最初刘易斯房贷证券的好点子\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Wall-street took a good idea: Lewis Raneiri's mortgage-bonds
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.74,1:51:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,变成了一个欺诈和愚蠢做成的原子弹\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And turned it into an atomic bomb of fraud and stupidity
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.38,1:51:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,现在原子弹马上就要毁灭全球经济了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That's on it's way to decimating the world economy
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.10,1:51:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的还挺像那么回事似的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}How do you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.80,1:51:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想到你现在还能笑的出来 我要是你的话可不这么乐观\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm glad you still have a sense of humor! I wouldn't if I were you!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.16,1:51:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,认识我的人都知道\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Now, Anyone who knows me, knows..
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.94,1:51:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是对别人的错误直言不讳的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}That I have no problem telling someone they're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.68,1:51:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（2008年3月14, 贝尔股票41点，39点）\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&} (2008 Mar 14) Bear at 41, Bear at 39
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.98,1:51:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你快看，股价还在往下泄\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's a disaster, it just says here
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.22,1:51:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但这一辈子，我是头一次… - 我的天\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}But for the first time.. in my life.. -Holy fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.84,1:51:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,…真心笑不出来\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's not so enjoyable
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.48,1:51:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的美国充斥着欺诈\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We live in an era of fraud in America
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.16,1:52:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅是银行，连政府也参与其中\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Not just in banking, but in government
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.06,1:52:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,教育，宗教\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Education, religion
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.42,1:52:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,视频，连棒球都作假\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Food, even baseball
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.36,1:52:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真正让我担心的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.22,1:52:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是说欺诈不道德\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Isn't that .. fraud is not nice
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.06,1:52:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是说欺诈很邪恶\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Or that fraud... is mean
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.36,1:52:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而是说，在过去一万五千年的历史中\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's that .. for fifteen thousand years
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.28,1:52:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,欺诈和短视就从来没有成功过\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Fraud and short-sighted thinking have never ever worked
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.80,1:52:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}  贝尔股价 37\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}  Bear at 37
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.64,1:52:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一次都没有 - 天哪\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Not once, eventually -Jesus
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.30,1:52:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 总会失败 - 已经降到37了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You'll get caught -We're at thirty-seven
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.76,1:52:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行情要下跌了 - 这哪是下跌，这是暴跌\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Things go south! -It's fucking plummeting man, it's fucking plummeting!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.26,1:52:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们难道都忘记教训了吗？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}When the hell did we forget all that?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.74,1:52:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为我们有希望，真的这么以为过\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I thought we were better than this, I really did
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.46,1:52:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And..
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.52,1:52:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我们不够明智 但是我也不觉得自己多么正义，多么骄傲\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The fact that we're not, doesn't make me feel all-right and superior!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.52,1:52:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是为大家感到…深深的悲哀\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It makes me feel... Sad.
