Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.96,1:53:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才你们正在谈话的时候 贝尔的股票已经跌落了38%\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}From the time you guys started talking, Bear-Stearns' stock is falling more than thirty-eight percent
