Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.54,1:55:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我很想去，谢谢你邀请我 - 总算打电话了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Yeah, I would like that, thank you very much! -Finally!
