Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.70,1:55:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这是跌破的趋势，我想和你谈谈脱身的事\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's in a free-fall decline, so I wanted to talk to you about pulling their money
