Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.92,1:56:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克我联系不上你 你能方便的时候尽快回电话吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mike I can't seem to get a hold of you, could you please call me at your earliest convenience?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.44,1:56:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是杰夫，你现在还要买股票？\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}It's Jeff, I.. eh.. You're buying stocks?
