Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.40,1:56:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的交友资料说我是个医学院学生 只有一只眼能用\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}My profile said that I'm a medical student with only one eye
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.40,1:56:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不懂社交\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}An awkward social manner,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.34,1:56:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,助学贷款还有14.5万要还\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}and 145 thousand dollars in student loans
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.60,1:56:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她的回信是\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}She wrote back...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.24,1:56:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我找的就是你这样的\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}You're just what I've been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.82,1:56:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她的意思是我很坦诚 那我也对你们开诚布公\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}She meant honest, so let me be honest...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.56,1:56:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,房地产危机是金融史上最大的机会\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}The housing-crisis represents the greatest financial opportunity
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.92,1:56:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但赚钱并不像我想象的那样简单\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Making money is not like i thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.16,1:56:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,做交易…杀死了生命中对我最重要的那部分 这部分和做交易无关\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This business... Kills the part of life that is essential! The part, that has nothing to do with business
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.08,1:56:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在过去两年，我内心感觉到，黑暗的东西在自我吞噬\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}For the past two years, my insides have felt, like they're eating themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.86,1:56:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经尊敬过的人\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}All the people I respected,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.48,1:57:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在再也不理我了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}won't talk to me anymore
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.24,1:57:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,除了通过律师来找我\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Except through lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.94,1:57:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人们…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}People...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.00,1:57:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,总希望有权威来告诉他们如何来选择价值 但他们选择权威\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Want an authority to tell them how to value things, but they chose this authority
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.68,1:57:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是基于事实情况，或者成就\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}not based on facts or... results
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.54,1:57:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们这样选，只是因为这些人看起来很权威 说出了他们想听的话\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They chose it because it seems authoritative...and familiar!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.48,1:57:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.26,1:57:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未盲从过大众\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}I'm not, and never have been.... familiar
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.08,1:57:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}So..
