Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.94,1:58:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这和我想象的不一样\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}This isn't how I pictured it
Dialogue: 0,1:58:45.92,1:58:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你以为是什么样的 - 反正不是这样\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}What do you think you'd find? -I don't know
