Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.42,1:58:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,马克，你听着吗\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mark, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.80,1:59:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,马克\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Mark?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.92,1:59:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,财政部长和美联储主席刚刚离开白宫\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Paulson and Bernanke just left the White House.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.40,1:59:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可能政府要出手了\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}There's going to be a bail-out
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.20,1:59:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不出手不行啊\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Well, they had to!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.54,1:59:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.08,1:59:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们用担保兑付房贷 - 这些人早就知道\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}We paid for mortgages with collaterals -They knew!
