Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.08,1:59:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这些银行家知道政府会用纳税人的钱保他们 他们不是愚蠢，他们只是不在乎\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}They knew the tax-payers would bail them out, they weren't stupid, they just didn't care!
