Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.90,2:00:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的几年，几百个银行和评级高管进了监狱\N{\fs30\c&HFFFF00&}In the years that followed, hundreds of bankers and rating-agency's executives went to jail.
